place.name: Rezervatia de Bujori de Stepa
place.description: 3,2 kilometers upward on rocky road to the Zau de campie peony botanical garden and nature reserve. It has the size of a large garden. The blooming between 15 april and 2 mai. The Paeonia tenuifolia L. can be located only in couple of places in eastern Europe.
